@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jbfrug(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(0.08)
    v0 = 0.23
    tmp = 0.79
    v1 = ((v0 * (tmp + 0.71 * v2 + 0.86)) + v1)
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = (v1 * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.54) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.10)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.57)) * (v1 - (tmp + 0.92 * tmp + 0.44)))
    v2 = (tmp - wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.56)))
    data[tid] = v0
